article_id:42,category_name:News,title_name:Issue when building both a Sweet Retreat and a Light Altar in the Castle Grounds[Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>It has come to our attention that when both the Sweet Retreat and Light Altar are built in the Castle Grounds, only one of these buildings&#39; stat boosts takes effect.</div><div><br></div><div>The event effect of the Sweet Retreat is functioning properly.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any further updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for your patience.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539855000"></span>]</strong></span><br><br>The above-mentioned issues have been fixed.</div><div><br>If you have already placed the Sweet Retreat, put it away into the Storehouse, and then place it again to have the stats boost effect take place correctly.<br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we gave out the following gifts to players who started the game before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539849600"></span>.<br><br>ãƒ»Quality Honey x10<br><br>These items can be received from your goodie box upon login until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540454340"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1539770100,update_time1540888472